26#pragma once
27
28#if ENABLE(NETWORK_CACHE_SPECULATIVE_REVALIDATION) || ENABLE(NETWORK_CACHE_STALE_WHILE_REVALIDATE)
29
30#include "NetworkCache.h"
31#include "NetworkCacheEntry.h"
32#include "NetworkLoadClient.h"
33#include "PolicyDecision.h"
34#include <WebCore/ResourceRequest.h>
35#include <WebCore/ResourceResponse.h>
36#include <WebCore/SharedBuffer.h>
37#include <wtf/CompletionHandler.h>
38
39namespace WebKit {
40
41class NetworkLoad;
42
43namespace NetworkCache {
44
45class SpeculativeLoad final : public NetworkLoadClient {
46 WTF_MAKE_FAST_ALLOCATED;
47public:
48 using RevalidationCompletionHandler = CompletionHandler<void(std::unique_ptr<NetworkCache::Entry>)>;
49 SpeculativeLoad(Cache&, const GlobalFrameID&, const WebCore::ResourceRequest&, std::unique_ptr<NetworkCache::Entry>, std::optional<NavigatingToAppBoundDomain>, RevalidationCompletionHandler&&);
50
51 virtual ~SpeculativeLoad();
52
53 const WebCore::ResourceRequest& originalRequest() const { return m_originalRequest; }
54
55 void cancel();
56
57private:
58 // NetworkLoadClient.
59 void didSendData(unsigned long long bytesSent, unsigned long long totalBytesToBeSent) override { }
60 bool isSynchronous() const override { return false; }
61 bool isAllowedToAskUserForCredentials() const final { return false; }
62 void willSendRedirectedRequest(WebCore::ResourceRequest&&, WebCore::ResourceRequest&& redirectRequest, WebCore::ResourceResponse&& redirectResponse) override;
63 void didReceiveResponse(WebCore::ResourceResponse&&, ResponseCompletionHandler&&) override;
64 void didReceiveBuffer(Ref<WebCore::SharedBuffer>&&, int reportedEncodedDataLength) override;
65 void didFinishLoading(const WebCore::NetworkLoadMetrics&) override;
66 void didFailLoading(const WebCore::ResourceError&) override;
67
68 void didComplete();
69
70 Ref<Cache> m_cache;
71 RevalidationCompletionHandler m_completionHandler;
72 WebCore::ResourceRequest m_originalRequest;
73
74 std::unique_ptr<NetworkLoad> m_networkLoad;
75
76 WebCore::ResourceResponse m_response;
77
78 RefPtr<WebCore::SharedBuffer> m_bufferedDataForCache;
79 std::unique_ptr<NetworkCache::Entry> m_cacheEntry;
80 bool m_didComplete { false };
81};
82
83bool requestsHeadersMatch(const WebCore::ResourceRequest& speculativeValidationRequest, const WebCore::ResourceRequest& actualRequest);
84
85} // namespace NetworkCache
86} // namespace WebKit
87
88#endif // ENABLE(NETWORK_CACHE_SPECULATIVE_REVALIDATION) || ENABLE(NETWORK_CACHE_STALE_WHILE_REVALIDATE)
